room_title: Escape room "Do Not Disturb" by Breakout Games - Cincinnati in Cincinnati
review: Game masters were helpful when needed which made the experience better. It was so fun that we ended up going back the next day to play a different room! We plan to make this happen at least once a month.

room_title: Escape room "Do Not Disturb" by Breakout Games - Cincinnati in Cincinnati
review: After a few escape rooms, the anticipation wears out just a little bit. I did the new "Do Not Disturb" room and was not too impressed. I expected more from a newer room. I have definitely done better. I also think the cost should be looked at more as they have gotten more expensive. Still a fun experience overall.
